data.description: Nestled in a picturesque setting in Amherst Township, this beautiful 3- bedroom, 2 bath colonial style home is a testament to timeless elegance and modern comfort. The farmhouse chic interior creates an inviting atmosphere that seamlessly combines rustic charm with contemporary convenience. Recent renovations have breathed new life into this property with new carpet adding warmth and comfort, new siding, and a brand new roof that's under a year old. Cozy in for some front porch seating or relax on your patio with a fire in the evenings.
